Name: Be aware of environment / internal Quince
Question: I know what keeps my colleagues busy commercially and privately, and use their knowledge, skills and passion for (my own) activities (projects)
Description: I know what keeps my colleagues busy commercially and privately, and use their knowledge, skills and passion for (my own) activities (projects)

Name: Have overview
Question: I can survey the various projects and sub-projects that Quince is dealing with, and also know which mutual coherence they have
Description: I can survey the various projects and sub-projects that Quince is dealing with, and also know which mutual coherence they have

Name: Understanding of commercial processes Quince
Question: I know where and who to address in order to have issues handled in time and of a qualitatively high standard
Description: I know where and who to address in order to have issues handled in time and qualitatively high-standing

Name: Can direct groups
Question: I can direct a random group of Quince employees and have them collaborate pleasantly
Description: I can direct a random group of Quince employees and have them collaborate pleasantly

Name: Task-oriented managing
Question: I achieve my objective/result by telling Quince employees which assignment they are working on, which task and responsibility they have at that, and monitor and/or correct the progress.
Description: I achieve my objective/result by telling Quince employees which assignment they are working on, which task and responsibility they have at that, and monitor and/or correct the progress.

Name: Delegate
Question: I can transfer my tasks and responsibilities to others, whereas I will keep the final responsibility.
Description: I can transfer my tasks and responsibilities to others, whereas I will keep the final responsibility.

Name: Time management
Question: I always survey which activities have priority, which are important, and always adjust my actions and time division to that.
Description: I always survey which activities have priority, which are important, and always adjust my actions and time division on that.

Name: Planning
Question: I can keep working effectively under time-pressure, pressure of several or difficult tasks, by the way in which I plan my activities.
Description: I can keep working effectively under time-pressure, pressure of several or difficult tasks, by the way in which I plan my activities.

Name: Dealing with stress
Question: I can keep performing effectively under time-pressure, pressure of several or difficult tasks, social pressure, setbacks, disappointments, opposition or crises
Description: I can keep performing effectively under time-pressure, pressure of several or difficult tasks, social pressure, setbacks, disappointments, opposition or crises

Name: Work accurately
Question: Usually I work without making many mistakes, and I always check my own work.
Description: Usually I work without making many mistakes and always check my own work.
